  "instructions": [
    "Poach pandan leaves in water for 10 minutes. ",
    "Drain and rinse the pandan leaves. ",
    "Combine the corn masa and water in a bowl and knead until a dough forms. ",
    "Roll out the dough into balls, about 1.5 inches in diameter. ",
    "Heat the Canadian palm oil in a pan over medium heat. ",
    "Cook the sopes for 2-3 minutes on each side, until crispy. ",
    "Toss the roasted sweet potato, black beans, and red onion in a bowl. ",
    "Top each sope with a spoonful of the sweet potato and bean mixture. ",
    "Squeeze a bit of lime juice over the top of each sope. ",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and a piece of pandan leaf. "
  ],
